page.title: 12Trewlands Cottages,Tiptree
page.content: Joel Brady and I went to Trewlands Cottages in Church Road, Tiptree. We went to no. one and a lady answered.We asked her four questions and she answered them all. How long have you lived here? 42 years. Have you liked living opposite Wilkins Jam Factory? Yes.Has it changed since you have been living here and what has changed? All the village is not as homely and I do not know as many people as I did. Are you well known to Wilkins? Yes very well. We went to no.two. 36 years, yes, no, Yes my husband and I worked there. Then we went onto no. three. 52 years, Yes my husband worked there, yes new people have come, Yes very well. Then we went to no. four. 60 years, Quite nice, an awful lot, I worked there.
